Restart a service on the specified remote

### Synopsis

{% endmarkdown %}
{% syntax text %}
cast services restart [OPTIONS] NAME 
{% endsyntax %}
{% markdown %}

### Required Arguments

__NAME__

The name of the service to restart


### Options

__--remote__ &lt;remote&gt;, __-r__ &lt;remote&gt;

The remote to use for this command

